OL,7,FBut the family of Mrs Hoskins revealed
OL,8,Flast month they had been contacted by
OL,9,Fofficials who said that Farrant was
OL,10,Fbeing considered for compassionate
OL,11,Fleave as he had been diagnosed with
OL,12,Fterminal cancer and could have months
OL,13,Fto live.
OL,15,FThe Multi-Agency Public Protection
OL,16,FArrangements (MAPPA) met earlier this
OL,17,Fweek to look at the case which the
OL,18,Ffamily say has been passed on to the
OL,19,Fprison governor to decide whether to
OL,20,Fmake a formal application for his
OL,21,Frelease.
