OL,7,FMrs Hoskins' three children Iain,
OL,8,FKatie and David Hoskins said in a
OL,9,Fstatement released to the PA news
OL,10,Fagency:
OL,12,F"We, as Glenda's children are
OL,13,Fextremely grateful for the support of
OL,14,Fthe general public who have either
OL,15,Fcommented on news articles, phoned
OL,16,Finto radio stations or have contacted
OL,17,Fus directly and all unequivocally
OL,18,Foppose Farrant's release on
OL,19,Fcompassionate grounds.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
