OL,7,F"We are all massively grateful for the
OL,8,Fsupport of MPs Penny Mordaunt, Kim
OL,9,FJohnson and Flick Drummond who have
OL,10,Fspoken out publicly and written to
OL,11,FAlex Chalk.
OL,13,FWant a quick and expert briefing on
OL,14,Fthe biggest news stories? Listen to
OL,15,Four latest podcasts to find out What
OL,16,FYou Need To Know...
OL,18,F"Our position remains that Victor
OL,19,FFarrant, if released, poses a clear
OL,20,Fand present threat, not only to us but
OL,21,Fthe public at large.
