OL,7,F"We are saddened and angry that his
OL,8,Frelease is even being considered and
OL,9,Fhe has shown no remorse for his string
OL,10,Fof crimes and terrorisation of women."
OL,12,FThe Ministry of Justice said in a
OL,13,Fprevious statement: "Glenda Hoskins'
OL,14,Fmurder was a horrific crime and our
OL,15,Fthoughts remain with her family and
OL,16,Ffriends.
