OL,7,F"Prisoners are only released on
OL,8,Fcompassionate grounds in exceptional
OL,9,Fcircumstances following strict risk
OL,10,Fassessments and no formal application
OL,11,Fhas yet been made in this case."
OL,13,FFarrant was jailed in November 1988
OL,14,Ffor a total of 12 years for rape and
OL,15,Fother offences, but just weeks after
OL,16,Fhe was released on November 7 1995, he
OL,17,Fsavagely beat Ms Fidler at her home in
OL,18,FEastleigh, Hampshire.
