OL,7,FSix weeks later, he murdered
OL,8,Faccountant Mrs Hoskins at her luxury
OL,9,Fwaterside home in Portsmouth by
OL,10,Fpushing her under the water in the
OL,11,Fbath.
OL,13,FHe left her body in the attic where it
OL,14,Fwas found by her 15-year-old daughter
OL,15,FKatie.
OL,17,FAfter killing Mrs Hoskins, Farrant
OL,18,Fwent on the run and was eventually
OL,19,Ffound in the south of France.
